            "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You aren't encumbered.</p><hr /><p>Whether expelling air or water, your siphons enable quick bursts of speed. You @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Leap], Stride, or Swim in a straight line, gaining a +10-foot status bonus to your Speeds during that movement. After you use Jet, you can't do so again for [[/r 1d4 #Recharge Jet]]{1d4 rounds}. You can't Jet in a vacuum and similar environments that lack air or fluid you can expel.</p>"
